Interface ErrorStateToModeMapping

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface ErrorStateToModeMapping
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Error State To Mode Mapping'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Error State
    • Mapped Modes
